comments: Recorded lecture was good. Daily quizzes were stressful but made you review the material

narratives.question_text:
Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
(Your anonymous response to this question may be viewed by Yale College students, faculty, and advisers to aid in course selection and evaluating teaching.)
comments: This class was a lot of Excel work, so be prepared for difficult PSETs if you take the class. Parts of it were useful like the lecture on taxes and 401ks but at times the class felt dry
